      "cooked": "<p>Nooooo please please Zeqo. Kush rri e numro <img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/images/emoji/apple/calendar_spiral.png?v=5\" title=\":calendar_spiral:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":calendar_spiral:\"></p>",
